{"tid":740691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界最英俊男鮮肉","createTime":"2018-07-13T05:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T08:47:37.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9a25a51d5d75c7828cb57a43b59db1275a2ea2a0","tid":740691,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"近幾年長相英俊、身材健壯的「小鮮肉」輩出。不過年齡卻下修無極限，網路上就瘋傳一位來自澳洲的「小鮮肉」，竟然只有13歲！<br />\n<br />\n這位小鮮肉叫做米勒(William Franklyn-Miller)，年僅13歲，不過卻擁有令人驚豔的「零死角」俊俏外表，擺起POSE，架勢更不輸國際男模。據了解，他現在已經是澳洲服飾業御用的童裝模特兒。他也因此在網上受到高度討論。不少網友看到他都驚呼「這臉是漫畫直接走出來的吧！」、「帥到不科學」、「這13歲我也可以」，更讚他的五官「鬼斧神工」、「上天最完美的作品」。也有人問「到底怎樣的父母有辦法生出如此高顏質的兒子」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201607/201607111772848_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201607%2F201607111772848_l.jpg&h=6d2156fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201607/20160711-227496_bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201607%2F20160711-227496_bm.jpg&h=83aa3f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201607/20160711-227497_bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201607%2F20160711-227497_bm.jpg&h=4224e08c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201607/20160711-227498_bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201607%2F20160711-227498_bm.jpg&h=d1dc144a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/photo/cts/201607/20160711-227499_bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fcts%2F201607%2F20160711-227499_bm.jpg&h=1052cb8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e78df6763abdece18b47542c8bd794607d1efa6a","tid":740691,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T05:31:58.000Z","msg